episodes.title: Answering the Big Question: Is Scientology a Cult?
episodes.description:
In this video, I answer questions from Ryder, a student working on a school project about Scientology. Drawing from my experience growing up in Scientology under the leadership of my uncle, David Miscavige, I discuss the line between religion and cult, the daily life of Scientologists, and the practices of the Sea Organization. I dive into topics like Scientology's manipulation tactics, brainwashing, financial exploitation, and disconnection policies, while sharing my journey of leaving a high-control group and exposing the truth.
